{
  "message": "test(fuzz): extend fuzz_scalar_cast corpus with 23 edge-case seeds\n\nAdd structured corpus seeds for scalar type casting edge cases:\n- null to each dtype (5 seeds)\n- bool conversions: true/false to int/float/utf8/null (5 seeds)\n- int edge cases: max/min/zero to float, int to utf8 (4 seeds)\n- float special values: inf/nan/neginf to int/float/bool (6 seeds)\n- utf8 to numeric: \"42\", \"-1\", empty string (3 seeds)\n\nIncludes batch unit test that replays all 23 seeds through the harness.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
